{{flavour|Projects a penetrating projectile with peculiar magical properties. It is randomly imbued with either fire or ice, and additionally will reflect from walls of any material due to the crystal embedded in the shot.}}

'''Crystal Bolt''' is a monster-only spell which launches an unusually reflectable bolt of [[fire]] or [[cold]] damage (50% chance of each). This bolt will bounce off of any surface, making [[multizap]]s a significant risk.

The following enemies cast Crystal Bolt:
*{{monsterlink|Crystal echidna}}
*{{monsterlink|Crystal guardian}}

==History==
*Crystal Bolt was removed in [[0.32]], replaced by [[Crystallizing Shot]].
*Crystal Bolt was added in [[0.14]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
